      "writtenOn": "2019-01-07T23:28:57Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "An alternative to storing info about the triggers in a DB would be to make TriggerPeriodicJobs natively idempotent. This would involve searching the Job DB (or cache) to see if a recent-enough Job already exists for each JobSpec (possibly ignoring forced jobs). For monitoring, we already have overdue_job_specs_s, which would catch failed triggers, although we would need to make some changes for it to work for weekly jobs.",
